{"tid":1157380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有線中國組]  農業部：不得擅自公布非洲豬瘟疫情","createTime":"2019-05-16T08:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T04:21:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9b664d32aec05ec6687905c78880a6335fe05e94","tid":1157380,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"【農業部：不得擅自公布非洲豬瘟疫情】<br />\n<br />\n農業農村部周四下發通知，有關非洲豬瘟病毒檢測結果由農業農村部及市場監督管理總局統一發布，其他單位和個人不得擅自公布相關訊息。<br />\n<br />\n各地若發現生豬產品或豬肉製品檢測結果為陽性，應及時將樣本送至國家非洲豬瘟參考實驗室進行覆檢，並在收到樣本日起5天內公布覆檢結果。<br />\n<br />\n#非洲豬瘟<br />\n#不得擅自公布<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"608d76e450e4f438fb95f6458640846e3916afed","tid":1157380,"uid":44171,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"又國家機密?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f929228f90729ed83e0b2a6874ff930569bd04af","tid":1157380,"uid":45518,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"最好唔好講, 發大個疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82490edd0c30b52fc86de6319e3f5372277370b3","tid":1157380,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"608d76e450e4f438fb95f6458640846e3916afed","tid":1157380,"uid":44171,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"又國家機密?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9610adcb6fe0db1c47f826572b2e7fa801673056","tid":1157380,"uid":81113,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"唐努烏梁海是不是中國國土？北京高院：中國人無權知道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/891137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/891137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f38e1281430a28b1e130b4643bf37aff9024b7cc","tid":1157380,"uid":54337,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":